---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';

const title = "Auto Repair Shop Valuation Calculator 2025 | Mechanic Shop Value & SDE Analysis";
const description = "Calculate your auto repair shop worth with our 2025 SDE analysis calculator. Get accurate mechanic shop valuation using proven industry multiples and benchmarks.";
---

<MainLayout title={title} description={description}>
    <div class="article-header" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50 0%, #3498db 100%); color: white; padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 30px;">
        <h1>Auto Repair Shop Valuation Calculator 2025</h1>
        <p>Complete SDE Analysis & Worth Assessment | Professional Mechanic Shop Valuation Services</p>
    </div>

    <div class="calculator-box" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <h2>Get Your FREE Auto Repair Shop Valuation Now!</h2>
        <p>Calculate your auto repair shop worth in under 5 minutes using our proven SDE methodology.</p>
        <a href="https://thevaluationgenie.com/" class="cta-button">Calculate My Auto Shop Value</a>
        <p style="font-size: 0.9em; margin-top: 15px; opacity: 0.9;">Free estimate â€¢ Professional $39 reports available</p>
    </div>

    <article>
        <section id="introduction">
            <h2>Introduction to Auto Repair Shop Valuation</h2>
            <p>Auto repair shop valuation is a specialized process that requires deep understanding of automotive service economics, equipment values, customer relationships, and industry-specific metrics. In 2025, the automotive repair landscape continues evolving with electric vehicles, advanced diagnostics, and changing consumer behaviors.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="sde-analysis">
            <h2>SDE Analysis for Auto Repair Shops</h2>
            <p>Seller's Discretionary Earnings (SDE) is the most accurate method for <strong>auto repair shop valuation</strong>. Unlike traditional businesses, auto repair shops have unique financial structures including equipment depreciation, parts inventory management, and technician compensation that require specialized analysis.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="faq">
            <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <div class="faq-item" style="background: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid #3498db; padding: 20px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;">
                <h4>What is the average auto repair shop valuation in 2025?</h4>
                <p>Auto repair shop valuations typically range from $200K to $5M+, with most shops valued between $400K and $1.5M. The exact value depends on shop type, location, equipment quality, customer base size, facility ownership, and financial performance. General repair shops average 2.0x-3.5x SDE, while specialty shops like import/luxury specialists can command 3.0x-5.0x SDE multiples.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </article>
</MainLayout>
